rows.label: fev04_120_195_msg0001
rows.name:
Finally, we actually get to depart
for Superbia.

rows.label: fev04_120_195_msg0002
rows.name:
Quite the strenuous detour
we ended up taking there.

rows.label: fev04_120_195_msg0003
rows.name:
Masterpon probably forgotten where
we even meant to get on ship.

rows.label: fev04_120_195_msg0004
rows.name:
Tora remember perfectly!
...Tenth floor, was it?

rows.label: fev04_120_195_msg0005
rows.name:
Goldmund not have half
that many floors!

rows.label: fev04_120_195_msg0006
rows.name:
It's the fourth floor.
Goldmund Flight Deck, to be precise.

rows.label: fev04_120_195_msg0008
rows.name:
Try to keep a tight hold on any
valuables, eh, Rex?
